", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，猜的，真了不起。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#2$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是位“灰禮帽”，你們的背後看來就是開斯特公爵了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......怪不得，她想要那把國劍。哼，她已經不再遮掩自己的野心了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你們的處境比我想像的還要糟糕。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜回到倫蒂尼姆，真的是想要爭奪王位嗎？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這你得問她自己，我不太關心。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#2$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你關心什麼？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可能更關心怎麼不把自己的衣服弄髒。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#2$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我回去，我會提醒母親要更加關注羅德島製藥的。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們之前太小看這家“醫療機構”了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，我看起來不像是個醫生嗎？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不像。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下次我會更努力點的。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們開誠佈公地談談吧，戴菲恩。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "溫德米爾公爵在這個地塊佈置了多少人？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我有兩個護衛，不過她們應該都死了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲剛封鎖這裡的時候，她們試圖帶我突圍，失敗了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩個護衛，真是一位親民的公爵繼承人。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們也盯上了那把劍嗎？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以放心，溫德米爾公爵對諸王之息沒有興趣，我可以向你承諾。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你為什麼會在這裡？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......巧合。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該知道，你欠我一次。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在可以離開這裡，我猜那位“灰禮帽”閣下很樂意和另一位大公爵的繼承人談談。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位一向以耿直善戰聞名的溫德米爾公爵，如果知道自己的女兒在薩卡茲包圍的地塊裡出了意外，她會怎麼做？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，無論是哪位大公爵，都很樂意看到自己的競爭對手率先與特雷西斯的軍隊不死不休。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我也可能是太過惡意地揣測外面的那位先生了，也許他會請你吃些點心呢？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很坦誠，伊內絲女士，你的這些源石技藝......確實救了我一命。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我被困在這裡確實只是一個巧合。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每位大公爵在倫蒂尼姆都有自己的情報網，無論是為了監視薩卡茲的動向，還是探聽其他大公爵的行動。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坦誠地說，後者比前者更重要。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是認為諾伯特區是個合適的藏身處而已。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更進一步，一位失蹤的王儲曾經身處的格拉斯哥幫，對於你而言是個有意義的情報來源。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這倒不是。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是和貝爾德......都喜歡去同一家影廳。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼——", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜，維娜還能拿著那把諸王之息在諾伯特區遊蕩，而沒有和劍一起被送到開斯特公爵面前......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是因為那位“灰禮帽”想用你們的力量為他自己解決些麻煩事。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是了，你們在找飛空艇。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實，沒有哪位公爵抵得住這樣的誘惑。就連我也很想知道薩卡茲是怎麼能造出一座飛在天上的要塞的，這會顛覆未來戰爭的形式。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們真的很愛這些，“戰爭”。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#10$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以為一位薩卡茲雇傭兵會同樣熱愛它。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我的確欠你們一次，那麼，可愛的醫生之家羅德島打算用我這條命做什麼呢？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我剛才說的，我在這裡沒有可供我差遣的護衛或者部隊，你大可以對此失望，伊內絲女士。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們和那位“灰禮帽”之間的麻煩事我沒有能力幫忙。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於那位先生和飛空艇的事，我們自己能處理好。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你要什麼？你很清楚我對於開斯特公爵的價值，卻還是救了我。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#4$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不會現在告訴我，其實你幫我一把的原因只是自己是個善良的好人吧？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#4$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，不是。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真可惜。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於我們而言，一位大公爵的力量確實難以抗衡。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比於羅德島，開斯特公爵恐怕應該把更多的精力放在別的事情上。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信，你可以說服你的母親幫這個忙。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這是個很高的要價。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們想借助我母親的參與來擺脫開斯特公爵的控制。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很清楚，這是在走鋼絲。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，這是我們可愛的醫生之家唯一能選擇的路。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#2$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g1_glasgowboxinggym", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道他們和那家酒店的談判是否順利。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#6$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許......我應該跟著去的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用擔心，阿米婭，那位伊內絲女士不會讓博士身處險境，更何況，只是借用他們的通訊站而已。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，這裡的病人也確實更需要我。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他們離開之前，我們已經約定好了撤離的時間。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們需要挺過薩卡茲駐軍的反撲，只要公爵們開始與薩卡茲交火，我們就可以抓住機會。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......計劃會順利進行的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......我只是稍稍有些不安。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#10$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡有一些......讓我感到壓抑的東西。我不知道那是什麼。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#10$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始，我以為只是諾伯特區的氣氛太過沉重，後來，我以為是......特蕾西婭小姐想要再度向我展現什麼。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可似乎都不是。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......阿米婭，我在本艦的時候，曾聽見有些薩卡茲稱呼你為“魔王”。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於你來說，這意味著什麼？你明明不是一名薩卡茲。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會希望自己是一個能帶領屬民的統治者嗎？還是個衝鋒在前的英雄？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王輕撫著身邊的諸王之息，這把劍仍然冰冷，一如往常。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不知道，推進之王小姐，我必須坦誠。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭小姐為我們所有人描繪了那麼一個未來......我仍然堅信，她所訴說的那個未來才是值得生活的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，她把這頂冠冕交給了我，卻沒有告訴我到底應該如何抵達那裡。如今，她甚至......站在了我們的對面。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能嘗試說服自己，這是她對我的考驗。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我其實沒有想好怎麼面對她。她會對我說什麼？她會怎麼看待我做的事情？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#11$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為自己選擇的道路......會讓她失望嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道自己是不是一個......值得被交付“魔王”權柄的人。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你仍然選擇承擔這份職責。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同樣在擔憂，自己無法成為那個人們期冀中的人。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個能夠劈開天災的英雄，那個能夠團結人民的君主......", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要怎麼才能做到？我要怎麼才能回應那些......如此沉重的期待？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拆毀一座圍牆嗎？還是說服幾個貴族？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "向人們呼喊？還是用沉默展露威嚴？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我並不擅長這些，高文也從不教我這些。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的大部分時間都是在格拉斯哥幫裡度過的，我所瞭解的，只是揍翻鬧事的酒鬼，或者帶著朋友們逃脫警察的追捕。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在羅德島，我學了些東西，可是這還是無法幫助我明白該如何行動。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我原以為......我回來了就能瞭解。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，當摩根領著那些市民，稱我為“殿下”的時候......我還是什麼都說不出來。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道該怎麼辦。我很慶幸，那只是個暫時安撫大家的把戲。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我如果真的正走在這條路上呢？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一開始只是，沒有辦法對這些痛苦的人視而不見罷了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......推進之王小姐，也許這就夠了。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭小姐曾告訴我，“魔王”不是一項職責。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......也只是不願意轉過身去而已。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g6_hotellobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島的博士，你喜歡自己的這份工作嗎？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "喜歡。;......;不喜歡。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line229", "option2": "line232", "option3": "line235"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line238"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，你自認為在做一些有意義的事情。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line238"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一個需要長久思考才能給出答案的問題嗎？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "3"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line238"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，你有比眼前事業更遠大的野心。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，我實在說不上喜歡我的這份工作。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人天生熱愛勾心鬥角，我也一樣。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有可能，我會靠自己貴族的名頭，在哪個偏僻的郡裡置上一大片土地，在壁爐前虛度一個又一個下午。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最好再養隻小牙獸，每天在莊園後面的林子裡散散步，思考些文學與詩歌之類的問題。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說來慚愧，我是個蹩腳的詩人，《倫蒂尼姆日報》的文學副刊上偶爾會登載幾首我的習作。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前的男人扶了扶他的帽子，甚至稱得上有些羞赧。"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "評論家們不以為意，我卻樂在其中。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我們都知道，那難以成為真正的生活，理想總難以成為真正的生活。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們被拋到了這個時代當中，就只能以這個時代所教育我們的方式行動。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，剛剛在這裡的是誰？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "羅德島的幹員。;這家酒店的經理和門童。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line262", "option2": "line262"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你清楚我說的是誰，羅德島的博士。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣吧，我們可以做另一場交易。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你帶著你的那位幹員離開這間酒店，繼續去執行我們之前談好的任務。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等到任務完成，我會把你和亞歷山德莉娜殿下引薦給公爵閣下。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是作為棋子或人質，而是作為客人與朋友。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們值得更深入的合作。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以放心，永遠兌現承諾是公爵閣下的信條。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "相比薩卡茲，你對一個維多利亞人更感興趣。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line280"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我們畢竟身在維多利亞。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別被她的表象所矇騙了，你以為這座地塊只是個薩卡茲搭建的可愛牢房嗎？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我並不覺得這裡可愛。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line288"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，淒慘牢房，隨你的便。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你們忙著宣稱自己是維多利亞的王儲，然後給那些感染者打針的時候，我也沒閒著。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是有些受折磨的倫蒂尼姆普通市民，可除此之外，還有更多——", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些小心藏起自己痕跡的人，那些別有用心的人。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我服務的那位公爵真心希望跨越磨難的維多利亞能夠重振榮光，可另一些人未必如此設想。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要把他們揪出來，這也是我的工作。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "而拯救這裡的市民卻與你無關。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line304"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜，你準備好了一些陳腔濫調用來指責我。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這當然與我有關，我全心全意地祝福每一個人都平安健康。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是這不可能，不是嗎？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有的人可以執著於現在，親力親為地改變每一件小事，但有的人必須承擔更重的使命，縱使這未必是他們自己的意願。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如，為一個國家尋找它能立足的未來。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我尊重前者，但我同樣希望你不要否定後者。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "每個大公爵都可以這麼聲稱。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line320"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "他們都認為自己在為國家尋找未來。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line322"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這就是維多利亞這場災難的源頭。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line324"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——我不否認。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些淺薄者會認為公爵們只是在為權力或者利益角力，看來你不在其中，羅德島的博士。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "權力只是手段，利益只是工具。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大公爵們真正爭奪的，是帶領這個國家走向未來的資格。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞已經蒙塵夠久了。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而薩卡茲們會成為擦拭維多利亞的砂紙，經過打磨，我們的國家會重煥榮光。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確實是個蹩腳的詩人，“灰禮帽”先生。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你終於來了，伊內絲小姐。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為我要等不到你了。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}